data.description: HUD Home nestled on a sprawling 2.1 acres. With 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, this residence offers a large living room ideal for entertaining. Step out onto the deck and drink in views of the property. Additionally, a mobile home ADU provides versatility, and the generously-sized shop is perfect for projects and storage. This home is a fixer upper but with some work you can experience the perfect blend of space and comfort in this serene setting.  Square footage was measured by an appraiser and varies from the tax records. Tax records show main home is 1729sq ft.  ADU info was estimated and should be verified if important.
